    <item>
      <title>拜登退出选举带来新混乱，金价上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-21/gold-climbs-as-us-election-chaos-escalates-after-biden-drops-out</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于市场权衡总统乔·拜登结束连任竞选的决定，黄金价格上涨，这引发了人们对此举是否会帮助或阻碍唐纳德·特朗普重返白宫的新疑问。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-21/gold-climbs-as-us-election-chaos-escalates-after-biden-drops-out</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 21 Jul 2024 23:03:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登退出美国竞选，大火威胁加拿大油井，油价上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-21/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-july-22</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于投资者权衡总统乔·拜登决定不竞选连任的影响，同时野火威胁到加拿大的一些生产，油价在周五暴跌近 3% 之后小幅走高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-21/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-july-22</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 21 Jul 2024 22:59:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登退出大选，美元和亚洲股市下跌：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-21/dollar-edges-lower-following-biden-s-election-exit-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[拜登结束竞选连任并支持副总统卡马拉·哈里斯后，美元下跌，亚洲股市下跌。中国央行下调了关键的短期利率。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-21/dollar-edges-lower-following-biden-s-election-exit-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 21 Jul 2024 22:55:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
